[ModBus Smart Meters] --> [GatewayXM-Agile-Stack] : data collection

package "Architectural Patterns" {
    [Service-Oriented Architecture] <<Pattern>>
    [Dependency Injection] <<Pattern>>
    [Publish-Subscribe] <<Pattern>>
}

